<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 15:12:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>前欧洲央行行长德拉吉试探企业以提高欧盟竞争力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/former-ecb-head-draghi-sounds-out-businesses-boost-eu-competitiveness-2024-01-10/</link><description>意大利前总理兼欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉周三在米兰会见了商界领袖，他正在准备一份关于如何提高欧洲大陆竞争力的报告。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 14:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/former-ecb-head-draghi-sounds-out-businesses-boost-eu-competitiveness-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫升级与中国关系，转向印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-upgrades-ties-with-china-amid-pivot-india-2024-01-10/</link><description>周三，在新当选总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖首次对北京进行国事访问期间，中国和马尔代夫升级了两国关系。此前，穆伊祖在竞选活动中将中国的地区竞争对手印度视为主权威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 14:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-upgrades-ties-with-china-amid-pivot-india-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺寄希望于新车型，梅甘娜降价以对抗法国特斯拉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-banks-new-models-megane-price-cut-fight-off-tesla-france-2024-01-10/</link><description>法国汽车制造商雷诺的一位高级官员周三对路透社表示，雷诺正指望推出新车型并降低梅甘娜车型的价格，以帮助其在本土与美国竞争对手特斯拉公司展开竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 14:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-banks-new-models-megane-price-cut-fight-off-tesla-france-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>2023年俄罗斯新车销量恢复至106万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-new-car-sales-recover-106-million-units-2023-2024-01-10/</link><description>俄罗斯分析机构 Autostat 周三的数据显示，随着该行业从制裁和许多外国汽车制造商退出中部分恢复，2023 年俄罗斯新车销量反弹至 106 万辆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 14:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russias-new-car-sales-recover-106-million-units-2023-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚首都遭纵火、抢劫，警察因欠薪罢工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-capital-hit-by-arson-looting-police-strike-over-missing-pay-2024-01-10/</link><description>巴布亚新几内亚州长表示，警察因工资问题罢工后，周三，商店和企业在巴布亚新几内亚首都遭到袭击和纵火，造成人员死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 13:55:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-capital-hit-by-arson-looting-police-strike-over-missing-pay-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>忠利集团收购当地合资企业 100% 股权，提升中国业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/generali-boosts-china-presence-by-acquiring-100-local-jv-2024-01-10/</link><description>意大利最大的保险公司Generali周三表示，将以约9900万欧元（1.08亿美元）收购当地合作伙伴中油资本的股份，从而获得对中国一家保险合资企业的完全控制权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 13:45:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/generali-boosts-china-presence-by-acquiring-100-local-jv-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构加倍承诺关注习近平的反腐行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-watchdog-doubles-down-vow-heed-xis-anti-graft-drive-2024-01-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，中国反腐监管机构加倍努力，承诺坚决执行习近平主席的命令，抓捕腐败和不忠的官员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 12:27:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-watchdog-doubles-down-vow-heed-xis-anti-graft-drive-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>Grifols 向 Gotham 寻求至少相当于股份损失的赔偿——董事会成员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-seek-compensation-gotham-least-equivalent-share-loss-board-member-2024-01-10/</link><description>西班牙制药公司 Grifols 的一名董事会成员周三告诉路透社，该公司将在其计划发起的诉讼中寻求至少相当于卖空者 Gotham City Research 周二报告所造成的股价损失的赔偿。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-seek-compensation-gotham-least-equivalent-share-loss-board-member-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>英国将部署军舰、航母进行印度洋联合训练</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-deploy-warships-aircraft-carrier-indian-ocean-joint-training-2024-01-10/</link><description>英国周三表示，随着两国加强安全关系，英国将在今年晚些时候向印度洋派遣军舰，并于 2025 年向该地区派遣一艘航空母舰，与印度军队进行联合训练和行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:48:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-deploy-warships-aircraft-carrier-indian-ocean-joint-training-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>Transneft：2023 年俄罗斯通过其网络的石油出口量下降 6.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/transneft-russian-oil-exports-via-its-network-down-65-2023-2024-01-10/</link><description>俄罗斯国家控制的石油管道垄断企业Transneft周三表示，去年俄罗斯通过其管道的原油出口量下降了6.5%，而2023年通过其网络的石油输送总量与2022年持平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/transneft-russian-oil-exports-via-its-network-down-65-2023-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：华尔街关注消费者物价指数和比特币波动，日本大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 11:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰表示，芬兰和中国国家主席讨论了管道损坏问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finnish-chinese-presidents-discussed-pipeline-damage-finland-says-2024-01-10/</link><description>芬兰总统绍利·尼尼斯托周三表示，他与中国国家主席习近平就去年连接芬兰和爱沙尼亚的波罗的海天然气管道遭受的损害进行了建设性会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:39:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/finnish-chinese-presidents-discussed-pipeline-damage-finland-says-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>行业协会：大众、丰田2023年中国市场份额萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-toyota-saw-china-market-share-shrink-2023-industry-association-2024-01-10/</link><description>周三的行业数据显示，随着传统国际汽车制造商将市场份额拱手让给中国竞争对手，大众集团和丰田汽车去年在全球最大汽车市场的份额出现萎缩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-toyota-saw-china-market-share-shrink-2023-industry-association-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年达沃斯：极端天气和错误信息是全球最大风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/davos-2024-extreme-weather-misinformation-top-global-risks-2024-01-10/</link><description>世界经济论坛（WEF）周三发布的一项调查显示，风险专家认为极端天气和错误信息最有可能在未来几年引发全球危机。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:42:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/davos-2024-extreme-weather-misinformation-top-global-risks-2024-01-10/</guid></item><item><title>印度莫迪在商业峰会上吸引投资者，企业公布巨额支出计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-pitches-growth-resilience-woo-investors-2024-01-10/</link><description>印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周三在其家乡举行的一次大型商业峰会上宣扬了印度的经济前景，马鲁蒂铃木和阿达尼公司公布了总价值近 300 亿美元的投资计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 08:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-pitches-growth-resilience-woo-investors-2024-01-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>